data.description: Beautiful Fully Renovated Ranch home in  Covington. Great for investors or retirees. This amazing Steeples entry Open floor plan with many updates, which include fresh interior paint and flooring, new granite countertops that compliment the SS appliances, new bathroom vanities and hardware, new lighting fixtures, and many more updates for this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom ranch that is on a large level lot with private Level backyard. Sit on the large Covered front porch, Nearby is easy access to Hwy 162/ Salem Rd.
